<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TACOS LOCOS 超狂塔可 | 台北花博亡靈節限定</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #0d0d13;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans TC", sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 680px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: rgba(20, 20, 30, 0.88);
            padding: 30px;
            border: 2px solid #ff007f;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px #ff007f, inset 0 0 10px #ff007f;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #ff007f;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px #ff007f, 0 0 20px #ff007f;
            font-size: 2.4em;
            margin: 0 0 8px;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #ff9900;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px #ff9900;
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: #00f0ff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px #00f0ff;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }

        .menu-section {
            border-top: 1px dashed #ff9900;
            padding: 20px 0;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .price-list {
            text-align: left;
            display: inline-block;
            line-height: 1.9;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .order-form {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            border: 1px solid #00f0ff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 18px;
        }

        .quantity-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 92px;
            gap: 12px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            color: #00f0ff;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .item-label {
            margin: 0;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: normal;
            line-height: 1.35;
        }

        input,
        select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            background-color: #1a1a26;
            border: 1px solid #ff9900;
            border-radius: 5px;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 1em;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        input:focus,
        select:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #ff007f;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px #ff007f;
        }

        .btn-submit {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #06c755;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(6, 199, 85, 0.4);
            transition: 0.3s;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin-top: 12px;
        }

        .btn-submit:hover {
            background-color: #05b34c;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 25px rgba(6, 199, 85, 0.7);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .notice {
            display: none;
            margin-top: 16px;
            padding: 12px;
            color: #111;
            background: #00f0ff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .faq-section {
            text-align: left;
            margin-top: 40px;
            border-top: 1px solid #333;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }

        .faq-title {
            color: #ff9900;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        @media (max-width: 520px) {
            body {
                padding: 12px;
            }

            .container {
                padding: 22px 16px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 1.85em;
            }

            .quantity-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 78px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>TACOS LOCOS 超狂塔可</h1>
        <div class="subtitle">台北花博「墨西哥亡靈節」期間限定攤位</div>
        <p>感受道地墨西哥亡靈節慶典，線上預訂、現場免排隊取餐！</p>

        <div class="menu-section">
            <h2>經典餐點</h2>
            <div class="price-list">
                脆皮塔可：$200<br>
                墨西哥餡餅：$200<br>
                起司玉米片：$150<br>
                墨西哥炸餃：$150
            </div>
            <p style="color: #ff9900; font-weight: bold;">必吃升級推薦：所有品項皆可加起司，讓你的餐點更邪惡！</p>
        </div>

        <form
            class="order-form"
            action="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfd1My3kk0aE_ienrbPuoXxKkUuxPavkLsIYsS5r4L3AhPwIg/formResponse"
            method="POST"
            target="hidden_iframe"
            onsubmit="orderSubmitted = true;"
        >
            <h2 style="margin-top:0; color:#00f0ff; text-align:center;">預約免排隊點餐選單</h2>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="customer-name">姓名</label>
                <input id="customer-name" name="entry.1316890237" type="text" placeholder="請輸入姓名" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="contact-note">備註 / 聯絡資訊</label>
                <input id="contact-note" name="entry.739709981" type="text" placeholder="例如：Email、IG 或其他備註">
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="phone">手機號碼</label>
                <input id="phone" name="entry.1125505816" type="tel" placeholder="例如：0912345678" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label>餐點數量</label>

                <div class="quantity-grid">
                    <p class="item-label">脆皮塔可</p>
                    <input name="entry.1227903265" type="number" min="0" value="0" required>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <div class="quantity-grid">
                    <p class="item-label">墨西哥餡餅</p>
                    <input name="entry.1408865256" type="number" min="0" value="0" required>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <div class="quantity-grid">
                    <p class="item-label">起司玉米片</p>
                    <input name="entry.1635484009" type="number" min="0" value="0" required>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <div class="quantity-grid">
                    <p class="item-label">墨西哥炸餃</p>
                    <input name="entry.274993264" type="number" min="0" value="0" required>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="cheese">是否需要在所有餐點上加起司？</label>
                <select id="cheese" name="entry.209708124" required>
                    <option value="否，不需加起司">否，不需加起司</option>
                    <option value="是，所有餐點皆加起司">是，所有餐點皆加起司</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="pickup-time">預計取餐時間</label>
                <select id="pickup-time" name="entry.428165537" required>
                    <option value="10:00">10:00</option>
                    <option value="11:00">11:00</option>
                    <option value="12:00">12:00</option>
                    <option value="13:00">13:00</option>
                    <option value="14:00">14:00</option>
                    <option value="15:00">15:00</option>
                    <option value="16:00">16:00</option>
                    <option value="17:00">17:00</option>
                    <option value="18:00">18:00</option>
                    <option value="19:00">19:00</option>
                    <option value="20:00">20:00</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <button class="btn-submit" type="submit">送出訂單</button>
            <div id="success-message" class="notice">訂單已送出！資料會同步進入 Google Form 回覆表。</div>
        </form>

        <div class="faq-section">
            <h2>常見問題 FAQ</h2>
            <p><span class="faq-title">Q: 塔可是什麼？</span><br>A: 是一種用薄餅包餡、方便徒手食用的墨西哥料理。</p>
            <p><span class="faq-title">Q: 塔可有辣嗎？</span><br>A: 可以有辣，也可以做不辣或微辣版本，可以客製調整。</p>
            <p><span class="faq-title">Q: 可以外帶嗎？</span><br>A: 大多數塔可都很適合外帶，因為本來就是方便拿取的街頭食物。</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <iframe name="hidden_iframe" style="display:none;" onload="if(orderSubmitted){showSuccessMessage();}"></iframe>

    <script>
        var orderSubmitted = false;

        function showSuccessMessage() {
            var message = document.getElementById("success-message");
            message.style.display = "block";
            orderSubmitted = false;
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
